name: Tezzy Everydays #1 | May 7th, 2021
description: This is the first day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I decided to go with an aquatic theme for today, as it's my dream to move to Marseilles with my wife. We live outside of Paris, but I often dream of the Mediterranean and the wonders that lie beneath its surface. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
